@AiliSarre

Yes, I fixed the whitespace and split the definition over multiple lines to keep it from being too wide. For future PRs, you should keep this in mind.

Normally I don't just push changes myself unless they're very minor, so you may see me comment with requested changes that you should then make, if you submit more entries. If you have other questions, you can submit them as an issue; you can tag me there, if you want.

